data.title: Film Constellation
data.text: When Rex, son of the King of Dinosaurs is suddenly snatched up and transported to the future in a faulty time machine, he finds himself stranded in the 21st Century. Desperate to return to his own era to help save his kin, Rex must team up with a gang of nerds, freaks and geeks to go back 65 million years in time. But when he realizes saving those he loves will prevent all other mammals from ever existing, Rex will have to face what it means to be ... The Last Dinosaur.
